nodes.text: A Maxillipede shuttle, commanded by Kraken, was unsuccessfully used to transport clone trooper Tup from Ringo Vinda to Count Dooku during the Clone Wars. However, Jedi General Anakin Skywalker, Clone Captain Rex and the ARC trooper Fives boarded the shuttle and destroyed Kraken and the droid crew before they could escape the system, rescuing Tup so he could be taken to Kamino for examination.
